-- Venezuela to raise Exxon dispute at OPEC meeting
-- 
-- Wed Mar 5, 2008 5:26am EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/03/05/us-opec-venezuela-exxon-idUSVAT00029320080305

 

 VIENNA  (Reuters) - Energy and Mines Minister Rafael Ramirez said he will raise Venezuela's dispute with Exxon Mobil ( XOM.N ) at OPEC's meeting later on Wednesday. 

 He reiterated his view that the major's move to freeze Venezuelan assets was a threat to all OPEC producers.